  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/a55bd5406d51554c7f84404818d73041.poster.avif?t=1729093646\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/a55bd5406d51554c7f84404818d73041.webm?t=1729093646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/a55bd5406d51554c7f84404818d73041.mp4?t=1729093646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Runes of Aereal is a fast-paced, horror-themed roguelike deckbuilder set in the shadowy lands of Aereal. Build your deck, and blitz through enemies with a combination of combo-centric cards and items as you explore the land in search of the Runes of Immortality. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deckbuilder Meets an RPG</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/342a33ced8cf4d336bd687f570a5942d.poster.avif?t=1729093646\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/342a33ced8cf4d336bd687f570a5942d.webm?t=1729093646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/342a33ced8cf4d336bd687f570a5942d.mp4?t=1729093646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Runes of Aereal combines deckbuilding and RPG elements- allowing players to choose from 6 characters with unique traits and abilities, making every playthrough immersive and unique.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Adventure Across the World of Aereal</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/73d935d79037b1f5433eedfbf00451f6.poster.avif?t=1729093646\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/73d935d79037b1f5433eedfbf00451f6.webm?t=1729093646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/73d935d79037b1f5433eedfbf00451f6.mp4?t=1729093646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the vast world of Aereal, visiting towns, unique locations and terrifying monstrosities- experiencing unique and rare events that mean no two runs are the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock New Combinations & Grow Your Power</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/21adfa4d4132b938a7d3b7a78576c099.poster.avif?t=1729093646\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/21adfa4d4132b938a7d3b7a78576c099.webm?t=1729093646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/21adfa4d4132b938a7d3b7a78576c099.mp4?t=1729093646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect new cards and magical items by slaying monsters, trading in cities, or, even, through Runes of Aereal’s crafting system - transmuting mundane treasure into powerful scrolls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/a55bd5406d51554c7f84404818d73041.poster.avif?t=1729093646\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/a55bd5406d51554c7f84404818d73041.webm?t=1729093646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/a55bd5406d51554c7f84404818d73041.mp4?t=1729093646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Runes of Aereal is a fast-paced, horror-themed roguelike deckbuilder set in the shadowy lands of Aereal. Build your deck, and blitz through enemies with a combination of combo-centric cards and items as you explore the land in search of the Runes of Immortality. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deckbuilder Meets an RPG</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/342a33ced8cf4d336bd687f570a5942d.poster.avif?t=1729093646\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/342a33ced8cf4d336bd687f570a5942d.webm?t=1729093646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/342a33ced8cf4d336bd687f570a5942d.mp4?t=1729093646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Runes of Aereal combines deckbuilding and RPG elements- allowing players to choose from 6 characters with unique traits and abilities, making every playthrough immersive and unique.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Adventure Across the World of Aereal</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/73d935d79037b1f5433eedfbf00451f6.poster.avif?t=1729093646\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/73d935d79037b1f5433eedfbf00451f6.webm?t=1729093646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/73d935d79037b1f5433eedfbf00451f6.mp4?t=1729093646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the vast world of Aereal, visiting towns, unique locations and terrifying monstrosities- experiencing unique and rare events that mean no two runs are the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock New Combinations & Grow Your Power</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/21adfa4d4132b938a7d3b7a78576c099.poster.avif?t=1729093646\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/21adfa4d4132b938a7d3b7a78576c099.webm?t=1729093646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2490310/extras/21adfa4d4132b938a7d3b7a78576c099.mp4?t=1729093646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect new cards and magical items by slaying monsters, trading in cities, or, even, through Runes of Aereal’s crafting system - transmuting mundane treasure into powerful scrolls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
